  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459530/extras/8dadcde5ee2848bdef1c19c3ffb91c8d.poster.avif?t=1612373007\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459530/extras/8dadcde5ee2848bdef1c19c3ffb91c8d.webm?t=1612373007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459530/extras/8dadcde5ee2848bdef1c19c3ffb91c8d.mp4?t=1612373007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Elastic Fantastic is a very difficult physics-platformer with a challenging game mechanic.<br>Use the unique elastic tie to connect to the floating rocks and fly yourself to the end!<br>You start with 60 lives so make them count.<br>Winning this game is a mountain of a task, only to be completed by the truly stubborn of heart and the most skilled of the gamers.<br><br>Watch out for the enemies!",
